extendedInfo.description: Learn the theory, try the problem, check the solution  - designed for students in AC &  DC theory. Suit electrical trade apprentices, electrical journeyman, automotive technicians, electronic technicians, mechatronics technicians, engineering and physics students.  Practice for your licence / exam by testing your knowledge of basic electrical / electronic circuits.More than 300 questions with topics including resistance, series circuits, parallel circuits, series/parallel circuits, capacitance, time constants, meter loading, meter shunts, multipliers, waveforms, inductance, transformers, reactance and series AC circuitsScores stored for future comparison.
